explanation: The inner loop used `for j in range(i):`, so it only compared each item to earlier items. That misses cases where a later item dominates an earlier one. Changing the loop to `for j in range(n):` ensures every pair (i, j) is checked (the j==i case won't trigger the strict condition), so any dominating pair will be found.
